  "detailed_description": "Nightmare Zone  is an Indie Horror Game made by two people. The dream World is like a big red room, with wooden doors on each sides: every door is a portal for a dream. Run Away from your Nightmares, explore all the areas of the dream World and find 5 doors in a row to escape. You can escape only if you can find all the doors.<br>Can you wake up? Something is looking for you and if you get caught you'll have to restart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c35af778ccc06a1177bcca0075037a7e.poster.avif?t=1745927632\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c35af778ccc06a1177bcca0075037a7e.webm?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c35af778ccc06a1177bcca0075037a7e.mp4?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Nightmare Zone is a challenge for the player: being able to complete the game can be frustrating, but that is precisely why completion can give great satisfaction! will you accept the challenge?<br>Will you be able to find in succession all 5 doors needed to wake up without getting caught by the demons that inhabit the nightmares?<br>Many others before you have tried to escape the Nightmare Zone. You'll have to be fast and brave to be among the lucky few to wake up again.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c635227b6aa02e1be2fc48de940966a2.poster.avif?t=1745927632\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c635227b6aa02e1be2fc48de940966a2.webm?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c635227b6aa02e1be2fc48de940966a2.mp4?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Nightmare Zone  is an Indie Horror Game made by two people. The dream World is like a big red room, with wooden doors on each sides: every door is a portal for a dream. Run Away from your Nightmares, explore all the areas of the dream World and find 5 doors in a row to escape. You can escape only if you can find all the doors.<br>Can you wake up? Something is looking for you and if you get caught you'll have to restart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c35af778ccc06a1177bcca0075037a7e.poster.avif?t=1745927632\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c35af778ccc06a1177bcca0075037a7e.webm?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c35af778ccc06a1177bcca0075037a7e.mp4?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Nightmare Zone is a challenge for the player: being able to complete the game can be frustrating, but that is precisely why completion can give great satisfaction! will you accept the challenge?<br>Will you be able to find in succession all 5 doors needed to wake up without getting caught by the demons that inhabit the nightmares?<br>Many others before you have tried to escape the Nightmare Zone. You'll have to be fast and brave to be among the lucky few to wake up again.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c635227b6aa02e1be2fc48de940966a2.poster.avif?t=1745927632\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c635227b6aa02e1be2fc48de940966a2.webm?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/c635227b6aa02e1be2fc48de940966a2.mp4?t=1745927632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
